{"tid":1470240,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"獸醫協會關注前線警犬受催淚煙影響健康","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:25:20.000Z","uid":177556,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ee80a3258572f1162b5bf3f79a7f7b3fb514d484","tid":1470240,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"香港獸醫協會發表聲明，對在前線工作的警犬及近日有獸醫診所內留院的寵物，受催淚煙影響表示極度關注。協會指，和警員不同，警犬並沒有任何防護裝備，但就被帶到充滿催淚煙的前線進行清場工作，對警犬的健康十分關注，建議警方考慮避免將警犬帶到有催淚煙的地方工作，或在出勤時為狗隻加上保護眼鏡和防毒面具等。<br />\n<br />\n協會指，產生催淚煙的化學物，可以造成動物流眼水、不停抓面部、嘔吐和咳嗽等，建議寵物主人為接觸到催淚煙的動物，用0.9%鹽水或清水徹底沖洗身體，抹淨地下和生活環境減少污染，若寵物有嚴重不良反應，應盡快帶到附近獸醫診所求醫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1152735&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1152735%26csid%3D261_341&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=6855669f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1152735&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b40b447262646985b4a2dab6abd973b956c267f7","tid":1470240,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca8cac6bf092b7aced1a98fdd6af762615e332e","tid":1470240,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"[基督徒入] 求求你地入機場Sing Hallelujah<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469121</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"794b30d31f972df282cce962d6a5f63c471f032a","tid":1470240,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/